nk" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u-t%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-10/poem-yFuKIz3dDm82pevdGS87ow">Tần Châu tạp thi kỳ 10 - 秦州雜詩其十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-xQbAS3msLllmTtVElPGw6g">Thái tang tử kỳ 09 - 采桑子其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/author-NkGwR6r3M3j5cQXaNNhfvQ">Phùng Duyên Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Trung-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-PESk2yP5aPwmK7kMdE4nwQ">Trung dạ - 中夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-V%C3%B4-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%C3%BAc-Long-H%C6%B0ng-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-wQZbA4jdvernqSpYpAUorg">Túc Long Hưng tự - 宿龍興寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-V%C3%B4-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-nNS9MUZKsgML_FtUAR25EQ">Kỳ Vô Tiềm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
